LARDD 1
TITLE PIIX3 IDE Driver File
TEXT Intel PIIX3 IDE / ATA-PIO DRFL 2 code file.
SECTION Files
ITEM drv-piix3ide.drfl -> DRFL 2 code file for PCI 8086:7010.
ITEM piix3ide.rxr -> install bundle containing drv-piix3ide.drfl and driverctl.rxe.
SECTION Install
ITEM rxr verify A:piix3ide.rxr
ITEM rxr install A:piix3ide.rxr
ITEM drivers reload
ITEM drivers show ata-pio
ITEM drivers
END
